{
  "stem": "2684.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So and they saw the tremendously big anti-gun columns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "An air raid game.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they bombard it to pieces.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And with them, they bombarded our section too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So out of, let's say, we had 10 rail, maybe two or three survived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The rest of them was-- and how?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I do not know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the door opened, and we could come out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And was no Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The next, the Germans was hanging out, bodies-- our railway truck was bodies from the bombardment, hundreds of bodies lying all around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started putting out-- whatever left, we start putting out to the open field.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And suddenly we found nothing-- no guards, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we found some sort of food in the German section.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because as they bombarded, they opened up-- pardon me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had tins, and they had something, biscuits and so forth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we picked up some sort of a food and start eating.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the instinct for life, we didn't talk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We just looked each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we started walking on the open field to watch the smoke.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And walking-- I mean, we were dragging, maybe a kilometer a morning and a kilometer in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know what distance we made.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, my extra, what I had in Dachau and from a little bit extra food left on me was gone, and I became the same muselmann than the rest.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started walking towards or sliding or however you want to call it towards the smoke and it started getting dark.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as it got dark, we start seeing [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] not cars, not even tanks, but vehicles coming towards us with caterpillar back and rubber front, which mean it wasn't heavy, heavy tanks.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
